story:
Title: The Digital Struggle

After the final bell rang, signaling the end of another long day at school, Sarah stepped out of the classroom with a heavy sigh. She adjusted her backpack on her shoulders and took a deep breath, preparing herself for the battle that awaited her at home.

Sarah was not what you would call tech-savvy. She struggled to navigate even the simplest of digital interfaces. Her friends often teased her about her outdated phone and computer, which were relics from a bygone era. But Sarah couldn't help it;
